From c8a6883137531f9c02a2527a7a943528318b512f Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: regksem <regksem@tuta.io>
Date: Fri, 19 Jun 2026 21:40:53 +0300
Subject: [PATCH] Move XWaterfall-specific classes into net.regksem.xwaterfall
 (patch 0076)

Relocate our own additions (MotdManager, AttackTracker, XWaterfallConfig,
ForwardingMode, CommandXWaterfall) out of the BungeeCord/Waterfall packages and
into a dedicated net.regksem.xwaterfall.{motd,conf,command} namespace, updating
all references. The public BungeeCord API (net.md_5.bungee) and upstream
Waterfall classes (io.github.waterfallmc, incl. WaterfallConfiguration) are left
in place to preserve plugin compatibility and keep upstream merges clean.

